## Test File Organization

```
tests/
├── unit/
│   ├── test_weights.py           # DimensionWeights, ProfileRegistry, knockouts
│   ├── test_brief.py             # Brief validation, inferred fields, diversity
│   ├── test_iteration.py         # Tier logic, oscillation, regression, ratchet
│   ├── test_cost_tracking.py     # CostCalculator, TokenUsageRecord
│   ├── test_failure_handling.py  # Retry, circuit breaker, failure diagnosis
│   ├── test_human_review.py      # Gate, urgency filter, trigger conditions
│   ├── test_evaluation.py        # Weighted scoring, confidence, conflict detection
│   ├── test_generator.py         # Generation, regeneration strategies
│   └── test_agents.py            # Version gating, interface completeness
│
├── integration/
│   ├── test_pipeline_happy.py    # Full flow → ad published
│   ├── test_pipeline_failure.py  # Full flow → ad abandoned after max attempts
│   └── test_circuit_breaker.py   # Circuit breaker integration with pipeline
│
├── fixtures/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── ads.py                    # Sample Ad objects
│   ├── briefs.py                 # Sample Brief objects
│   ├── evaluations.py            # Sample EvaluationResult objects
│   ├── mock_responses.py         # Mock Gemini and Claude API responses
│   └── database.py               # Test DB setup and teardown
│
└── calibration/
    └── test_calibration.py       # Real API calls — run manually with -m calibration
```

